ğŸ©¸ Blood Bank Management System (Django)

    A Django-based Blood Bank Management System that helps manage blood donors, blood requests, blood stock, and emergency donor notifications.
This project focuses on real-time blood availability, admin-controlled workflows, and secure user authentication.

âœ¨ Key Features
ğŸ‘¤ User Features

User Registration & Login
    Secure Authentication
    Forgot Password with OTP verification
    Password Reset
    Donor profile with:
    Blood Group
    Mobile Number

ğŸ§‘â€âš•ï¸ Admin Features

Admin Dashboard
    View all blood requests
    Approve / Reject blood requests
    Automatic blood stock update
    Find compatible donors
    Send emergency email notifications
    30-minute cooldown timer after sending donor emails
    Manage blood stock quantity
    ğŸ©¸ Blood Request Flow
    User submits blood request
    Admin checks stock
    If stock available â†’ request approved
    If stock unavailable â†’ compatible donors notified via email
    Donor search locked for 30 minutes

